                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">McCormick</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-01-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 11, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. McCormick reports that sworn statements from the owners only of the cargo on
                    the <hi rend="italic">Arabia</hi> relating to facts stated in Department’s
                    telegram of the 7th instant are required for formal presentation to the
                    admiralty court.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
